		(company "Gonoboben/plataVM")
		(comment 1 "V1.6 PCB-D boundary: two-phase buck baseline, local control/ADC and CAN-FD")
		(comment 2 "Detailed hierarchy 41..46; no controller, MOSFET, magnetics, connectors or footprints selected")
	)
	(lib_symbols)
	(text "40_POWER_5V_TOP - V1.6 HIERARCHY MAP\nPCB-D converts PACK_BUS_P5_IN to 5V_SYS_BUS and distributes ten protected 5 V outputs.\nOUT1..OUT7 are controlled; OUT8..OUT10 are Always-On monitored in RUN.\nPreliminary converter target: two-phase synchronous buck, 15 A continuous / 20 A short."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 12 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.30 1.30)) (justify left))
		(uuid "p5-v16-40-101")
	)
	(text "LOCAL CONTROL / TRANSPORT\nPCB-D contains local I/O/ADC and a CAN-FD node. Normal converter/output commands and detailed current/fault/temperature data are CAN-FD objects.\nP5_GROUP_SAFE_OFF and P5_GROUP_HARD_OFF are direct hardware inputs; P5_BOARD_FAULT_N is a direct summary output."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 84 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.10 1.10)) (justify left))
		(uuid "p5-v16-40-102")
	)
	(text "SUB-SHEETS 41..46\n41 converter; 42 output template; 43 OUT1..OUT5; 44 OUT6..OUT10; 45 local diagnostics/data aggregation; 46 output/CAN/hard-line connector boundary.\n5V_SYS_BUS does not power PCB-B critical rails and is not supplied by EMG."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 150 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.08 1.08)) (justify left))
		(uuid "p5-v16-40-103")
	)
	(text "FAIL-SAFE / THERMAL RULES\nLocal protection remains active without CAN-FD. SAFE/HARD_OFF override normal commands and Always-On status.\nOutput 3 A ratings apply only within the total converter, copper and thermal budget. Efficiency, ripple, transient response and cooling require calculation."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 212 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.08 1.08)) (justify left))
		(uuid "p5-v16-40-104")
	)
